Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.20,0:00:29.75,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛が愛を「重過ぎる」って理解を拒み
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.92,0:00:34.55,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憎しみに　変わって行く前に…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.69,0:00:36.52,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもそうだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.64,0:00:41.54,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,バツの悪い事情にはいつも蓋して
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.65,0:00:44.37,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食わせ物のリアル
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.48,0:00:46.70,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歪んだジレンマ時代で
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.85,0:00:50.46,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束したはずの二人さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.60,0:00:54.94,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,気付かず通り過ぎて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.61,0:01:02.56,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壊しあって　解り合ったことも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.74,0:01:04.37,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,置き去りにした
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.49,0:01:07.81,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,これが成れの果てなの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.94,0:01:12.35,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認めないで　立ち向かったときも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.96,0:01:18.56,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落ちて行く時のイメージから逃げ出せずに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.70,0:01:23.30,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah　何度でも探し出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.40,0:01:30.05,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君の目　その手の温もりを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.27,0:01:35.39,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛はいつも私を傷つけるだけ…って君はつぶやいて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.50,0:01:40.05,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信じる事が怖くて泣いたんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.24,0:01:42.30,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱さを知って強くなれ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.45,0:01:46.06,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐れず信じることで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.18,0:01:51.08,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本当の愛を知るだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.20,0:00:29.75,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛說愛「過於沉重」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.92,0:00:34.55,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在轉變成恨之前　把它拒絕於心門之外…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.69,0:00:36.52,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬物皆是如此吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.64,0:00:41.54,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是把不合時宜的事隱藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.65,0:00:44.37,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是冒牌貨的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.48,0:00:46.70,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在扭曲了的窘迫時代
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.85,0:00:50.46,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連本應定下約定的兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.60,0:00:54.94,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都會毫無察覺地擦肩而過
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.61,0:01:02.56,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那開始崩壞但曾經互相理解的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.74,0:01:04.37,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將其撇下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.49,0:01:07.81,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂的末路嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.94,0:01:12.35,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中不服　想與之對抗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.96,0:01:18.56,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要從當初墮落的印象中逃離開去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.70,0:01:23.30,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　就算歷經千百次也要找出
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.40,0:01:30.05,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的雙眸　你手中的余溫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.27,0:01:35.39,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小聲嘟囔著「愛總是讓我遍體鱗傷…」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.50,0:01:40.05,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因畏懼堅信不疑的事而哭過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.24,0:01:42.30,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道軟弱才能變強
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.45,0:01:46.06,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要害怕堅信不疑地走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.18,0:01:51.08,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才是愛的真諦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.86,0:00:04.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在四年前阿扎提斯坦爆發的內亂中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.46,0:00:07.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾與Celestial Being的成員有接觸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.45,0:00:10.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於那時的事  我應該早在四年前就說明了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.87,0:00:13.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜時過境遷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.68,0:00:19.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今Gundam新機型的出現  再次使你成為焦點人物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.35,0:00:24.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿扎提斯坦王國第一公主  瑪麗娜·伊斯邁爾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.56,0:02:02.02,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}#03  阿里路亞奪還作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.49,0:02:04.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,議會已經通過了\N聯邦保安局設置直屬獨立治安維持部隊的提案
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.75,0:02:07.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預計建立規模達四千萬人的軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.50,0:02:13.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有吠陀的情報搭載才能使此創設成真
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.13,0:02:15.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能盡微薄之力是我的榮譽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.55,0:02:20.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦政府不會放任任何微弱的抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.30,0:02:23.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是為了即將來到的「大和」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.62,0:02:25.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我期待著你們的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.83,0:02:27.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是自然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.34,0:02:31.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們正是為此而誕生的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.88,0:02:39.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忠實地實行著伊奧利亞·修亨伯格的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.18,0:02:41.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡人是做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.66,0:02:45.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做到的只有我們  改革者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.82,0:02:52.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今都對阿扎提斯坦的公主放任不管
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:54.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你現在又打起了什麼算盤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.59,0:02:57.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明心裡很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.43,0:03:00.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們會來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:02.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然會來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.17,0:03:06.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡還囚禁著Gundam Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:12.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒  實驗體E-57
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.11,0:03:21.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四年裡一直被監禁於此的Gundam機師  就是這個男人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.42,0:03:31.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並沒有受到我腦量子波的影響
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.91,0:03:36.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具報告上說  是由於其頭部受傷所致
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:37.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.36,0:03:41.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於又見面了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.58,0:03:46.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然還活著啊  瑪麗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.11,0:03:48.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.64,0:03:53.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我啊  在收容所一直和你說話的阿里路亞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.64,0:03:53.44,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（這裡的收容所，指超人機關對少年實驗品進行培養的場所）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.59,0:03:55.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不叫瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.30,0:04:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  你就是瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:02.25,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,0)}拉格朗日1  資源衛星群
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.55,0:04:06.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有駕駛MS的作戰經驗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.68,0:04:07.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能會有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.23,0:04:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只駕駛過作業用的工程機器人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.22,0:04:14.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那那傢伙  居然帶了這麼個門外漢回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.59,0:04:16.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說啊  還有很多事要做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.43,0:04:18.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多多關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.68,0:04:20.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可愛的教官大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.22,0:04:22.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.81,0:04:29.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊爾·迪蘭地…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.51,0:04:35.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蕾娜  Arios和Cherudim修整的如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:36.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在進行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.90,0:04:38.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:40.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍舊把自己鎖在房間裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:45.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想表明自己不打算回Celestial Being吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.70,0:04:51.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如記錄所顯示的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.58,0:04:55.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Throne進行著與我們有所不同的武力介入
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:04:57.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道想說你們不是同伴…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:04:58.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.59,0:05:08.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管如此  你們同樣用Gundam殺了人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:11.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,許多人像我一樣收到了噩耗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.21,0:05:14.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的所作所為必然招來仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.01,0:05:16.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.97,0:05:19.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界本來很和平
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.54,0:05:22.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安樂的日子本來可以繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.91,0:05:26.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你們毀了我的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.74,0:05:31.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只希望自己一個人的和平嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.70,0:05:33.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.55,0:05:37.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  誰都不想變得不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.42,0:05:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉  轉到A-LAWS有什麼不適應的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.30,0:05:45.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼特別的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.68,0:05:48.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是訓練量比平常更多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.76,0:05:49.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.29,0:05:53.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校  在超人機關相關資料中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.82,0:05:55.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有位叫瑪麗的人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.25,0:05:58.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗？不  我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.27,0:06:02.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有回收的資料我應該都過目了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.01,0:06:03.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.79,0:06:08.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有任務來了  先掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.87,0:06:09.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:10.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:14.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉  主力部隊來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.16,0:06:19.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  一旦收到聯絡  全員各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:20.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.70,0:06:25.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據任務計劃  採取警備姿態
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.54,0:06:27.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯絡先頭部隊的佩麗絲中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.97,0:06:28.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.78,0:06:32.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長翅膀的駕駛員
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.69,0:06:34.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被監禁在那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.02,0:06:40.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把人交給上級後就毫無音訊了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:44.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS卻知道此事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:47.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如Level 2情報所提到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.96,0:06:49.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認Meister仍然生還
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.85,0:06:51.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS也在聚集
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:53.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該如何是好呢  小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.06,0:06:57.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我們這邊來應對吧  你可以回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.84,0:06:58.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.94,0:07:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗  你為什麼改了名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.25,0:07:08.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有那種言行…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.89,0:07:12.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是另一種人格…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.28,0:07:15.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王留美發來的暗號通信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.80,0:07:18.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在人革領反政府勢力收監設施中…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.39,0:07:20.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現了阿里路亞·哈普提茲姆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.43,0:07:23.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道   這個人是Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:25.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.57,0:07:27.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被聯邦抓住了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.54,0:07:29.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得找不到他的蹤跡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.28,0:07:32.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特  全員召集
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.40,0:07:33.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行情況介紹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:36.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？找到阿里路亞了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.19,0:07:39.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里路亞？這人是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.79,0:07:41.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是同伴  是同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:43.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里路亞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.28,0:07:50.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.23,0:07:54.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼停止搜尋Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.82,0:07:56.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒這個必要了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.92,0:07:57.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒必要了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.26,0:08:01.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎司令部給Celestial Being放了誘餌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.95,0:08:03.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然對不起地面部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.74,0:08:07.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這是瞭解對方戰鬥力的絕佳機會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.97,0:08:11.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的找到阿里路亞了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.13,0:08:15.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  王留美來的精確情報
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.43,0:08:17.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來開始進行救援作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.87,0:08:19.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救援作戰  打算怎麼做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.84,0:08:22.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望由你來策劃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:25.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇·李·諾瑞加
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.57,0:08:27.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請為我們進行戰術預報
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.19,0:08:29.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.76,0:08:33.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他若能歸隊  就能實現四架Gundam同時作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.06,0:08:35.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這樣心裡還是沒底啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:37.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.86,0:08:38.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,助我們一臂之力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.21,0:08:40.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都是為了救出阿里路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.85,0:08:45.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐  給你這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.97,0:08:48.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.41,0:08:51.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別把期待強加於我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.42,0:08:55.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的預測…改變不了任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.53,0:08:58.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只會讓大家陷入危險的境地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.01,0:09:01.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不會後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.37,0:09:06.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算任務失敗了  也不會怪罪於你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.18,0:09:13.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們無論如何都想救出阿里路亞救出同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.29,0:09:18.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了  為我們佈置戰術吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.88,0:09:27.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特  稍後能把現有戰鬥力和具體數據給我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:28.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.62,0:09:40.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王留美發來了詳細資料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.50,0:09:44.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害  連被監禁的人和地點都這麼清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.42,0:09:47.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.62,0:09:52.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要抑制這條航線的粒子光束的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.07,0:09:58.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  萊爾·迪蘭地的能力竟如此之高
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.00,0:10:00.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.49,0:10:03.50,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}OO  Seravee  Cherudim發射準備
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.89,0:10:03.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於到實戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.82,0:10:05.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不認為你會有出場的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.10,0:10:07.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我還省心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.01,0:10:10.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艙內似乎很吵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.98,0:10:12.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟想要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.45,0:10:12.07,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}進入戰鬥模式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.44,0:10:14.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救出同伴  救出同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:16.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.38,0:10:18.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰開始  作戰開始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.11,0:10:20.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要打仗了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.82,0:10:23.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seravee  裝備專用火箭炮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.77,0:10:29.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然能啟動Twin-Drive
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.93,0:10:31.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但仍不安定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.32,0:10:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過度使用TRANS-AM哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.11,0:10:33.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:38.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐發來了任務計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.65,0:10:41.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  這計劃是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.13,0:10:43.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真夠大膽的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.38,0:10:46.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅三百秒的閃電作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.42,0:10:50.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是皇·李·諾瑞加
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.27,0:10:54.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  也有我的戲份啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.94,0:10:57.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  這樣一來更方便了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.09,0:10:59.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指什麼？  指什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.00,0:11:01.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自言自語而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.69,0:11:04.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就拜託你支援我了  哈羅喲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.66,0:11:09.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普特利麥奧斯  進入大氣圈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.65,0:11:12.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OO  Seravee  Cherudim  出擊準備
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.65,0:11:12.74,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Cherudim Gundam：GN-006 智天使高達，\NDynames的強化機型）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.29,0:11:16.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0043  開始任務
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.70,0:11:19.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arios保持出擊狀態  待機中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.70,0:11:19.10,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Arios Gundam：GN-007 墮天使高達，\NKyrios的強化機型）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.72,0:11:22.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.05,0:11:23.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.38,0:11:26.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王留美的報告中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.67,0:11:29.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在監禁阿里路亞的地方出現了這個名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.69,0:11:32.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜她…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.83,0:11:38.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜·伊斯邁爾和阿里路亞關在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.13,0:11:40.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Field散佈到最大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.44,0:11:43.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始進入大氣圈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,==================
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.13,0:11:51.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校  菲拉德觀測點來電
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.87,0:11:53.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說捕捉到了突入大氣圈的物體
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.00,0:11:55.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是運送艦規模的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:11:59.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太莽撞了  竟然連宇宙船一起降落到地面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.45,0:12:03.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備炮擊  MS部隊也趕快做好出擊準備
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.52,0:12:05.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩麗絲中尉  敵襲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.44,0:12:07.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你前往確保E-57
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.19,0:12:08.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.30,0:12:14.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.19,0:12:14.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.20,0:12:15.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS機庫被…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.99,0:12:16.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動作快！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.18,0:12:21.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C、Celestial Being的宇宙船…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.71,0:12:22.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全炮發射！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.27,0:12:29.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然不減速？  難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:31.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Field最大幅度展開
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.01,0:12:34.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密潛水模式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.40,0:12:41.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝進海裡去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.28,0:13:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵…敵艦開始潛入水中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.24,0:13:10.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用導彈迎擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.73,0:13:11.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.45,0:13:15.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種狀況  是要打粒子光束的主意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.08,0:13:23.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那  特瑞亞  粒子光束的擴散時間大約是300秒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:25.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在此之前將阿里路亞救出
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.60,0:13:26.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.41,0:13:27.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三分鐘就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.71,0:13:29.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下兩分鐘再救一個人如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.35,0:13:32.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.15,0:14:01.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.70,0:14:03.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種震動是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.48,0:14:12.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵方MS追上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.40,0:14:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cherudim  炮狙擊戰開始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.86,0:14:17.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打不中也無妨  進行牽制吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.38,0:14:19.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.45,0:14:24.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  哈羅  哥哥在戰鬥時會說些什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.20,0:14:26.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狙擊目標  狙擊目標
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.42,0:14:28.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.85,0:14:31.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cherudim Gundam  洛克恩·斯托拉托斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:32.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狙擊目標
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.48,0:14:41.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好驚人的粒子量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:43.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡要死守住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.58,0:14:50.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能再靠近一點的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.67,0:14:56.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一步也不能退後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:02.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  攻擊從別的方向來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.17,0:15:05.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cherudim  擊墜了敵機
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.32,0:15:06.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他原來不是門外漢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.25,0:15:10.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.91,0:15:12.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打中了  打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.82,0:15:14.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運氣而已  運氣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.09,0:15:21.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  沒辦法靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.92,0:15:23.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救援部隊那邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.03,0:15:29.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.56,0:15:35.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡塔隆嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.91,0:15:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡交給下官  中尉請前往確保E-57
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.12,0:15:39.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.56,0:15:43.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  卡塔隆在營救犯人？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.22,0:15:46.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們和Celestial Being聯手了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:51.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.51,0:16:05.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那  你怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:08.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那個地點去  Arios馬上就到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.84,0:16:09.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arios？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:11.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.97,0:16:23.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現阿里路亞了  將Arios…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:26.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛好  Arios進行彈射
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.94,0:16:31.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密  再次下潛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.69,0:16:38.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續以GN導彈進行牽制  前往匯合地點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.86,0:16:40.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還剩下…120秒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.47,0:16:46.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人們被放出來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.93,0:16:51.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是刹那他們做的  那到底是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.09,0:16:57.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是指定地點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.25,0:17:10.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.59,0:17:13.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.33,0:17:18.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止了  實驗體E-57
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.22,0:17:24.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面發生戰鬥了嗎  為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:25.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽得到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.98,0:17:26.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離門遠一點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:28.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠一點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.36,0:17:37.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.57,0:17:39.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.44,0:17:47.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後30秒也快用盡了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.29,0:17:50.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.39,0:17:52.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別動！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.45,0:17:53.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.46,0:17:55.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不叫那種名字！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.67,0:18:01.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  這才是你真正的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.43,0:18:05.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗  瑪麗·帕法西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.05,0:18:09.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗·帕法西？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.86,0:18:12.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗  瑪麗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.41,0:18:23.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的幻覺是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.00,0:18:24.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.98,0:18:28.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖跟我們走吧  E-57
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.08,0:18:32.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉  您沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.23,0:18:36.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那  阿里路亞  沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.58,0:18:37.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.69,0:18:38.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.16,0:18:41.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗明明就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.68,0:18:43.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里路亞  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.96,0:18:46.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里路亞  阿里路亞！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.37,0:18:50.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.01,0:19:05.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗  我一定會來接你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.83,0:19:06.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.27,0:19:14.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam有三台？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.28,0:19:23.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.20,0:19:30.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.28,0:19:49.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.05,0:19:50.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要追擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.43,0:19:53.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要優先確保設施的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.50,0:19:54.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.03,0:19:59.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam脫離  開始撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.57,0:20:03.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務結束  任務結束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.10,0:20:09.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼  總算結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.05,0:20:11.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們成功救出同志了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.05,0:20:15.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是多虧了GIN1的情報啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.37,0:20:17.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.76,0:20:23.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席琳  我聽過參加救援部隊的成員的報告了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.29,0:20:25.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.85,0:20:33.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說其中一位成員在設施中目擊到了阿薩迪斯坦第一公主\N瑪麗娜·伊斯邁爾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.37,0:20:34.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪…瑪麗娜她？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.01,0:20:36.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被囚禁了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.75,0:20:37.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.52,0:20:39.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.45,0:20:43.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我們沒能救出她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.00,0:20:44.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:51.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但根據報告  瑪麗娜公主被疑似Celestial Being的成員帶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.86,0:20:54.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶走了？  被Celestial Being？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.97,0:21:00.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.50,0:21:05.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜…
